# Data Assimilation (PetscDA)

The `PetscDA` object provides a high-level framework for data assimilation capabilities.

It currently only provides ensemble-based data assimilation capabilities for combining model forecasts with observations in dynamical systems.
It centralizes ensemble storage, observational metadata, and user-defined forecast/analysis operators, enabling algorithms to run independently of MPI layout or vector/matrix backends.
